snippet.description: After a brownie kills a man with semen a confused Private Investigator must YOLO his way through a Spaniard's Picnic to find the truth.

snippet.title: The Spaniard's Picnic - 5sf Invades London
snippet.description: This is the consolation prize for the US women's Olympics volleyball team. If you get beaten by Brazil, you are forced to spend an oddly-subtitled picnic with a strange man who claims to be Spanish and a volleyball. Silver medals, as it turns out, are just harder to come by these days.

snippet.title: The Charmed Life of Daniel Yolo
snippet.description: Sensing his popularity waning within days, Daniel tried transferring to an all-idiots school in the neighboring city, but failed to gain admittance when he correctly named three colors and two numbers.

snippet.title: Confused Dick
snippet.description: In traditional noir narratives, the Femme Fatale often leads the Detective down a dark, seedy path, from which the only escape is opening the closet door.

snippet.title: CSI: CHICO
snippet.description: It appears this semen...(sprays semen all over face)...is I have semen on my face. Yeeah.

snippet.title: Kelsey's Diet
snippet.description: Sometimes the liquid diet truly is the best option, by which I mean drown yourself in a pool or ocean full of liquid because you're too fat to live.

snippet.description: They make the butterflies work naked too, just so they can't smuggle any glitter with them back to their rainbow hives on Lisa Frank Mountain.

snippet.description: Teen pop stars and bored NBA attendees have been training all their lives for this moment: The chance to be on camera eating a hot dog while some losers compete for a silly medal.

snippet.title: What's For Dinner?
snippet.description: Pro tip: Getting out of the oven and securing your freedom is a lot easier if you look delicious with a glass of red and a side of grilled asparagus.

snippet.title: Slow Poke
snippet.description: "Last Minute Week" comes to a close with this sad look into a debilitating condition, made all the more humiliating when your friends insist on having the bathroom door open at all times. (Thanks for the prompt, @AleGleser, and thanks to everyone who submitted. We have enough great ideas from y'all for another 433 weeks, but alas all good things must come to an end. See you next time!)

snippet.title: Depressed Balloon Artist
snippet.description: In this changing economy, people aren't looking for skilled balloonists anymore. They're not even looking for skilled Rubik's Cube jugglesolvers -- though admittedly, that's a much cooler party trick. However, the best party trick of ALL is attempting to wash away your sorrows in hard whiskey and failing at it. (This prompt courtesy of @NixWesthoff)

snippet.title: Knife Club
snippet.description:
We meet on Wednesdays to find out about hot new knives everyone's talking about, do a little catching up, and of course have a bit of wine. Every now and then, a few people forget the rule about stabbing in the back, but otherwise it's a gas. (Today's prompt brought to you by @Hobcockie)

Send prompts every night this week (starting around 10:30pm-PST) to @5sf !!!

Their squabbles last long into the night, so loud and constant that the neighbors took to recording them all, and preserving them in an embarrassing documentary entitled "Shut Up Little Sandwich." It screened at Sundance and got decent reviews. (Prompt courtesy of @johnebosworth)

snippet.title: 5secondfilms Week In Review #194
snippet.description: Bandits are stealing baby videos to fund NASA's spy program which lost its budget trying to turn non-alcoholic beer into double mustache juice.

snippet.title: Double Mustache
snippet.description: The ladies go crazy for one 'stache. But if you hit 'em with the ultra-rare double-fuzz multi-lip-ticklin' combo 'stache attack, it's practically a license to cream jeans. I hate what I just wrote, good night.

snippet.title: Non-Alcoholic Beer
snippet.description: Nothing gets the blood pumping into Rage Mode quite like the smooth crisp taste of non-alcoholic beer. Or, for that matter, beer. Beer triggers Rage Mode pretty easily too.

snippet.title: Spy Cam
snippet.description: Thankfully, the Russian Premier was fairly shortsighted, and the live violin music at the gala was probably loud enough to cover up the constant metal clanging. On the other hand, the fellow absolutely hated dancing with men, so their super-nifty spy plan kind of stumbled out of the gate. Man, did they get some great-looking footage, though.

snippet.title: Paul's Baby Video
snippet.description: Don't answer the phone. Don't look at the TV. And whatever you do, for God's sake, do not make copies of it and show it to other people. Because seriously, it's just gross and you could ruin someone's appetite for the rest of their day.

snippet.title: Made Out Like Bandits
snippet.description: Then they got caught, and had to make out like prisoners. It was only an hour later when one of them got the bright idea to make out like escape artists, and soon enough they were back on the streets, making out like lions or something.

snippet.title: Best. Day. Ever.
snippet.description: After a long day (or even month) of bad press and relationship woes, there's truly nothing like a thetan-clearing rubdown from your local masseur. Wait, masseuse. I meant masseuse.

snippet.title: Historically Correct BBQ
snippet.description: The party inevitably took a turn for the worse just a few minutes ago, when one of the British guests looked at an assortment of food and drink on the table, and remarked over how the hosts should have paid more for it. The Americans were so angry, they practically felt like throwing the entire food table off the deck -- and indeed, one of them flicked his potato chip over his shoulder in rage.

snippet.title: Pubert The Orphan Boy With The Tiny Locker
snippet.description: Things got hard for Pubert ever since his parents met their fiery fate in a snake petting zoo. Girls wouldn't talk to him, for example. The administration actively pranked him by giving him miniature or otherwise inferior school equipment. Even President Obama called up the superintendent just to make it known how much he hated Pubert.
